org.anchoranalysis.bean.shared.path

Class RootPath

  • Object
    • AnchorBean<RootPath>
      • RootPath

  • public class RootPath
extends AnchorBean<RootPath>
    Defines a *root path* i.e. a directory in which files are read/written during analysis

    Analysis scripts may select different root-paths depending on how they are executed (during debugging, locally/server)

    The name of a root must not be unique, but the combination of all fields should be unique i.e. several roots can have the same name, but should vary in their other settings

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
